step_data.thought: The user wants to zoom in to select a smaller area for exporting as OpenStreetMap XML Data. The current state of the page shows that the 'Zoom In' link has been clicked multiple times, and the map is now at a higher zoom level. To achieve the goal of selecting a smaller area, we need to zoom in further. Since clicking the 'Zoom In' link multiple times has not increased the zoom level sufficiently, we will continue to click it to zoom in further.
